Know they go for the low, they comin' in where you at (Bitch)

[Verse 2: Comethazine]
30 round drum to the chest, it's a big AK
Bullet holes [?] through the back (Boom)

150 shots, never lack
Bitch, I sleep with the strap, stay strapped up
